cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV 

The paper is about a model for efficient retrieval in information retrieval systems, which is a subfield of computer science. Therefore, cs.IR is the most likely category. The paper also deals with natural language processing tasks, which falls under cs.CL. The model proposed in the paper involves training strategies and network layers, which are related to machine learning and deep learning, respectively, and hence cs.LG and cs.AI are also likely categories. Lastly, the paper uses data from a search engine, which suggests that it may also be related to computer vision and image processing, and hence cs.CV is a possible category.
